  "text": "Estrone conjugates (E 1 C) and PdG in urine samples were determined by microtiter plate EIAs as previously described by us [CITATION_1] . The intra-and interassay coefficients of variation were 7.3 and 8.0% for E 1 C, 7.5 and 8.5% for PdG, respectively.",
